full_description:

Speaker:: Sara Jakša

Track: PyCon: Web
OAuth simplified and secured third-party integrations for the end user. But for the developer of the integration, it can still present some friction. This talk talks about examples of real-life problems that were encountered by implementing multiple OAuth integrations.


Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2022 conference, April 11-13 2022.
https://2022.pycon.de
More details at the conference page: https://2022.pycon.de/program/XKJYW3
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin
Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
